summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Twenty-eighth Avenue Northwest, from West 65th Street to West 70th Street, et al, in the City of Seattle, by constructing watermains to under Ordinance No. 19551, creating Local Improvement District No. 1883 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
